entities.createSql: CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `${TABLE_NAME}` (`logMessageId` INTEGER PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT NOT NULL, `sessionId` INTEGER NOT NULL, `message` TEXT NOT NULL, `className` TEXT NOT NULL, `functionName` TEXT NOT NULL, `lineNumber` INTEGER NOT NULL, `logType` TEXT NOT NULL)
CREATE VIRTUAL TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `${TABLE_NAME}` USING FTS4(`message` TEXT NOT NULL, content=`LogMessageDto`)
contentSyncTriggers: CREATE TRIGGER IF NOT EXISTS room_fts_content_sync_LogMessageDtoFts_BEFORE_UPDATE BEFORE UPDATE ON `LogMessageDto` BEGIN DELETE FROM `LogMessageDtoFts` WHERE `docid`=OLD.`rowid`; END
CREATE TRIGGER IF NOT EXISTS room_fts_content_sync_LogMessageDtoFts_BEFORE_DELETE BEFORE DELETE ON `LogMessageDto` BEGIN DELETE FROM `LogMessageDtoFts` WHERE `docid`=OLD.`rowid`; END

CREATE TRIGGER IF NOT EXISTS room_fts_content_sync_LogMessageDtoFts_AFTER_UPDATE AFTER UPDATE ON `LogMessageDto` BEGIN INSERT INTO `LogMessageDtoFts`(`docid`, `message`) VALUES (NEW.`rowid`, NEW.`message`); END

CREATE TRIGGER IF NOT EXISTS room_fts_content_sync_LogMessageDtoFts_AFTER_INSERT AFTER INSERT ON `LogMessageDto` BEGIN INSERT INTO `LogMessageDtoFts`(`docid`, `message`) VALUES (NEW.`rowid`, NEW.`message`); END
